## 사용자 검색/자동완성

### API

```
GET /api/v4/users/autocomplete?term=검색어&team_id=team123
```

```
POST /api/v4/users/search
{
    "term": "검색어",
    "team_id": "team123",
    "allow_inactive": false
}
```

### 구현

```go
func (a *App) AutocompleteUsersInTeam(teamId, term string, ...) (*model.UserAutocomplete, *model.AppError) {
    // username, nickname, first_name, last_name 검색
    users, err := a.Srv().Store().User().Search(teamId, term, ...)
    
    return &model.UserAutocomplete{
        Users: users,
    }, nil
}
```

